text:
Projects
Path: /projects/&lt;project name&gt;
Created on request to share data with other members of collaborative project.

Archive
Path: /archive/labs/&lt;name&gt; & /archive/users/&lt;user&gt;
Intended for long term storage of data that is no longer being used for analyses. This directory is not created by default and must be requested by a PI.

